quran[7{c,v,t}:
2,170,aur jab un logon se kaha jata hai ke jo ( kitaab ) khuda ne nazil farmai hai is ki pairwi karo to kehte hain ( nahi ) balkay hum to isi cheez ki pairwi karen ge jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya. bhala agarchay un ke baap dada nah kuch samajte hon aur nah seedhay raste par hon ( tab bhi woh inhen ki taqleed kiye jayen ge )
2,171,jo log kafir hain un ki misaal is shakhs ki si hai jo kisi aisi cheez ko aawaz day jo pukaar aur aawaz ke siwa kuch sun nah sakay. ( yeh ) behray hain gungay hain andhay hain ke ( kuch ) samajh hi nahi satke
2,172,ae ahal imaan jo pakeeza cheeze hum ne tum ko ataa farmaen hain un ko khao aur agar khuda hi ke bande ho to is ( ki nematon ) ka shukar bhi ada karo
2,173,is ne tum par mra howa janwar aur lahoo aur soor ka gosht aur jis cheez par khuda ke siwa kisi aur ka naam puraka jaye haraam kardiya hai haan jo nachar hojaye ( bashart e kay ) khuda ki nafarmani nah kere aur hadd ( zaroorat ) se bahar nah nikal jaye is par kuch gunah nahi. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala ( aur ) reham karne wala hai
2,174,jo log ( khuda ) ki kitaab se un ( aayton aur hdayton ) ko jo is ne nazil farmai hain chupatay aur un ke badlay thori si qeemat ( yani dunyawi Manfiat ) haasil karte hain woh apne piton mein mehez aag bhartay hain. aisay logon se khuda qayamat ke din nah kalaam kere ga aur nah un ko ( gunaaho se ) pak kere ga. aur un ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab hai
2,175,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat chore kar gumraahi aur bakhshish chore kar azaab khareeda. yeh ( aatish ) jahannum ki kaisi bardasht karne walay hain !
2,176,yeh is liye ke khuda ne kitaab sachaai ke sath nazil farmai. aur jin logon ne is kitaab mein ikhtilaafkiya woh zid mein ( aakar neki se ) daur ( hogaye ) hain
